ActPilotage Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of LOUIS RHÉAUME of Sillery, Quebec, as a member of the Laurentian Pilotage Authority to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Jean-Louis Dufour, whose term has expired.
